(145, 1, '2016-11-17 19:29:56', '2016-11-17 19:29:56', 'Welcome to <a href="http://maikalaal.com/">maikalaal.com</a> for enjoying some nonsense and sarcastic humor which promise to make your day with some stomach pain laughs and gags. We will bring to you the most trending news with a spicy twist which will be digested with fun. Join our lively spirit website and keep yourself awake with a healthy smile on your face with most funnier and fashionable humor surrounding your ear.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_148" align="alignleft" width="258"]<img class="wp-image-148 " src="http://maikalaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/welcome-maikalaal-300x199.jpg" alt="welcome maikalaal" width="258" height="171" /> welcome maikalaal[/caption]\r\n\r\nWe will express our emotions with a young spirit to make an impact on the social world. Explore us for the latest buzz with an electrifying content which will give you a heart warm shock. Never fail to miss our forthcoming notifications in the form of visually impressive images, content, and videos. Some awe-inspiring facts to boost your skills with knowledgeable information.\r\n\r\nDemonetization of 500/1000 currency is such a pain in the ass for rich bastards.\r\n\r\nRich monkeys were seen scratching their heads all night for the black money they have kept under their beds. Such a waste of hard earned money!!! But Modi strict step shocked the whole nationthis is a small problem of 1 or 2 days for every Indian citizen.but for rich people its time to pay some TAX.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Narendra_Modi" target="_blank">Narendra Modi</a>s bold step to eliminate black money from India is getting applauded worldwide. But some politicians are crying for the decision taken for the demonetization of currency for the reason that their looted money has turned into a garbage. All the political parties are getting teamed up against PM Modi, but the citizens are calm and respecting the fact that this is a good step.\r\n\r\n[